Step 1: Create IAM Policy

Go to:
👉 AWS Console → IAM → Policies → Create policy

📄 JSON Policy

Paste this:

{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": ["secretsmanager:GetSecretValue"],
      "Resource": "*"
    }
  ]
}

👉 Click Next → Name it



