Terraform Drift:-  mismataches between terraform state and actual infrastructure

terraform plan -detailed-exitcode

1. Apply → Infra created
2. Manual change → Drift
3. Pipeline → Detect drift
4. Apply → Block 
5. Fix drift → Apply 
6. Destroy → Block if drift 


